not restricted to merger remnants or galaxies with close\ncompanions; instead, a larger population of wider separation pairs exhibit\nenhanced star formation due to recent close encounters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 May 2013 17:54:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 May 2013 17:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
