so to single dish telescopes with deformation\nproblems. This work also forms the basis of the upcoming science results of\nAMiBA-13.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 May 2013 03:09:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-09"}
